               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipit of Texts I-III; initial lines of section of Text I; titles of books to be read; titles or initial lines of prayers; some words: halle luya (fols.), bǝḍuʿ (fols. 37r), fǝtuḥa; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numbers.&#xD;
On the incipit page of Texts I and III (fols. 1r and 61v) and on fol. 28r, a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</rubric>
